Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.68,0:02:02.47,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,不器用でぎこちないほど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.89,0:02:05.47,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,愛しく始まるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.77,0:02:07.58,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,give me an answer
