Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.81,0:21:59.08,ENJP,NTP,0,0,0,,真っ直ぐに歩いてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.74,0:22:07.16,ENJP,NTP,0,0,0,,不器用なこの心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.99,0:22:21.68,ENJP,NTP,0,0,0,,偽りないその目に映る暖かい光りを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.68,0:22:26.73,ENJP,NTP,0,0,0,,溢れる希望の中で今僕ら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.00,0:22:32.18,ENJP,NTP,0,0,0,,どれだけの愛に出逢えるのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.18,0:22:38.99,ENJP,NTP,0,0,0,,同じ時を今生きている愛すると
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.30,0:22:44.33,ENJP,NTP,0,0,0,,思う喜び に触れて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.81,0:21:59.08,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,筆直地一路走來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.74,0:22:07.16,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我這顆笨拙的心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.99,0:22:21.68,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,感受著你的真誠雙眼所發出的溫暖光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.68,0:22:26.73,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,沐浴在滿溢而出的希望中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.00,0:22:32.18,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我們究竟能遇見多深沉的愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.18,0:22:38.99,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,一起活在當下 愛在此時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.30,0:22:44.33,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,如此想來 不禁欣喜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.02,0:02:25.02,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,475)\fad(0,800)}我和朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.13,0:02:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算在一起相處了十年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.41,0:02:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有我所不知道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.53,0:02:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算知道生日是幾號
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.39,0:02:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算知道內褲的花紋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有兩人的秘密基地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.14,0:02:41.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也還有很多不知道的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.95,0:02:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你不明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你把期待已久的計劃作廢 跑來守著我爸的手術
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也完全不會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:02:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是大和的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.18,0:03:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同時 也是阿砂父親動手術的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.68,0:03:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還以為你是看門人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.28,0:03:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂 叔叔的手術是從幾點開始？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.27,0:03:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.32,0:03:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替我向大和同學問聲好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然否決了一堆餿主意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.89,0:03:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我覺得無論你做什麼那孩子都會高興的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:49.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好好加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:03:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂 和你一起精心制定的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.58,0:04:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會成功實現給你看的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.34,0:04:11.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.05,0:04:15.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 久等了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.68,0:04:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好喜歡她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼時候來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:22.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛才到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.84,0:04:24.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.31,0:04:26.99,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}約定時間是10點沒錯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.33,0:04:28.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天起得好早 4點左右就醒來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡回籠覺後又被遲到的夢驚醒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.44,0:04:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果才到了5點鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和 生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 嗯 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:50.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡你 大和
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.96,0:04:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天包在我身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.66,0:04:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.99,0:04:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去哪呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間很充裕 我們就走著去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.25,0:05:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行程是我和阿砂一起想出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:19.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天沒下雨太好了 好高興哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和阿砂一起..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.62,0:05:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.33,0:05:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.34,0:05:35.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡好有趣哦 玩什麼好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.17,0:05:38.27,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}保齡球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保齡球..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到一塊去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.37,0:05:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到一塊了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.77,0:05:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.57,0:05:58.66,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}害羞害羞害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.14,0:06:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學的球好重..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你拿的很輕鬆..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可能拿不動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.21,0:06:17.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 猛男同學好厲害 手好大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.62,0:06:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 猛男同學好厲害 力氣好大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.39,0:06:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.48,0:06:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.44,0:06:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.82,0:06:37.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思看一下短信哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.01,0:06:38.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是菜菜子發來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.90,0:06:40.12,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:41.83,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.98,0:06:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以看哦 沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:44.63,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.16,0:06:49.63,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.79,0:06:50.38,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}OK
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學 可以一起拍張照嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:06:57.64,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}主題 Re：凜子生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:06:57.64,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:06:57.64,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}我和猛男同學在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:06:57.64,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}保齡球超有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:57.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這樣會不會太臭美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.03,0:06:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.56,0:07:20.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留瓶位置好奇怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:23.67,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣子好難哦 第二輪能補中嗎..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.22,0:07:25.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和一直在笑呢 好開心的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂他說..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:34.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論我帶你去哪你都會開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可沒有那麼乖巧哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.16,0:07:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的很開心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:48.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠和猛男同學一起過生日
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.22,0:07:50.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很開心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.42,0:07:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一樣 很開心很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很幸福啊 大和
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.47,0:07:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 我知道這家店哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.77,0:08:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有在書裡看到過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.52,0:08:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直很想來一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.70,0:08:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為價錢很貴 所以沒什麼機會來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.47,0:08:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有打工所以沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋糕閃閃發光的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是看著就讓人好開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.79,0:08:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.42,0:08:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我因為大和閃閃發光的笑容而開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂他說..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你喜歡做點心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.43,0:08:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那肯定也喜歡吃點心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.14,0:08:35.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎 阿砂還真是善解人意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.75,0:08:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.11,0:08:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.86,0:08:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砂川同學長得這麼帥 感覺應該很受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:43.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會沒有女朋友呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.84,0:08:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:47.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得他說覺得很麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.16,0:08:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:09:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學也很帥 還好沒有女朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能和猛男同學交往 我真的很幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸運的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.68,0:09:12.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝您生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Happy birthday to you~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Happy birthday to you~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:24.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Happy birthday 親愛的大和醬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請在吹蠟燭之前許願吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.66,0:09:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？那那那那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.22,0:09:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Happy birthday to you~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:41.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望明年 後年 大後年的生日都能和猛男同學在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用說出來也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.29,0:09:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是本店第一位把願望說出口的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難為情死了 闖禍啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.09,0:09:50.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂 我已經如你所說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.97,0:10:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和大和過得很幸福哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.11,0:10:05.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以..牽手嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:13.46,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}猛烈心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.35,0:10:14.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:21.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然很緊張呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.84,0:10:32.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是猛男同學事先通知店裡我生日的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 阿砂叫我這麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是砂川同學？太感謝他了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.42,0:10:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 砂川同學為了猛男同學做了很多努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.93,0:10:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好朋友真令人羨慕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砂川同學今天在做什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.93,0:11:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂他..阿砂他..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.08,0:11:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔的手術是從幾點開始？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:06.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.87,0:11:08.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好好加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.85,0:11:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.03,0:11:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和 今天的計劃是和阿砂一起想出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.90,0:11:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡門票都買好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.28,0:11:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可以的話 你跟朋友一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.34,0:11:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去阿砂那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂的爸爸 今天要做手術
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.59,0:11:53.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.58,0:11:55.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人在區立醫院 2點開始手術
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.05,0:11:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然阿砂叫我別去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.59,0:12:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我想來想去還是想去他那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.44,0:12:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢 恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.25,0:12:08.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.70,0:12:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼這麼重要的事情不跟我說呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,區立醫院是在車站那邊吧 得趕緊出發呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.64,0:12:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會照著這個去天文臺的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們一起為我制定的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會好好去玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學趕緊去陪著砂川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學在身邊的話 一定會讓他安心不少的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要快點出發才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要用跑的哦 猛男同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.17,0:12:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和 這是禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.30,0:12:49.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你收下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:12:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝你降生於世
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:21.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝你出現在我面前..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.44,0:13:30.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手術室在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分娩室在3樓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.47,0:13:35.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為您孩子要生了..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.36,0:13:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 我就預感你會來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.07,0:14:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:09.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和第一個女友的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明那麼期待的說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說的親戚家的叔叔呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.61,0:14:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.32,0:14:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.76,0:14:21.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手術要花幾小時？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.90,0:14:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道阿砂想做些什麼 在想些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.95,0:14:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不懂什麼是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我是你的朋友 就讓我陪在你身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:45.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,..爸爸 他生來就心臟不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.62,0:14:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是爸爸啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.71,0:14:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我和姐姐出生的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.40,0:14:54.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說他一直很擔心會遺傳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而得知我們都很健康的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:15:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽說他高興得都哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這個原因
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他總是很寵 很疼愛我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從來沒見過爸爸生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.36,0:15:16.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手術..這次是第二次了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.13,0:15:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老實說情況蠻危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.79,0:15:20.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他病發的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽和姐姐出門旅行不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.34,0:15:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家裡只有我和爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:30.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那天放學還繞去逛了書店 聽了CD..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回來之後看見爸爸倒在地上..孤零零一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.59,0:15:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不知道他昏倒多久了 我..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是早點回家就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.07,0:15:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果沒出門的話 說不定就不會發生這種事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.71,0:15:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.83,0:15:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你一個人這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.38,0:15:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.15,0:16:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.66,0:16:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你姐姐你媽媽你爸爸都不會這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂可能不是不說..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.40,0:16:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是說不出口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本次手術是將你父親自身的瓣膜進行修復的瓣膜成形術
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,術後再內服抗凝結劑 如果沒出現心律不齊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.66,0:16:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果呢？成功了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定成功了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.91,0:16:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成..成功..了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.81,0:17:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太用力了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.72,0:17:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.61,0:17:04.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.18,0:17:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.03,0:17:08.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 讓你一個人扛著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.93,0:17:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 誠 這些天讓你受苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.89,0:17:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 完全不會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.20,0:17:14.25,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微冷靜一下吧 爸爸他沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.35,0:17:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 猛男也在這裡啊 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.44,0:17:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後的事讓媽媽和姐姐來做就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誠和猛男 你們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.29,0:17:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我丈夫的情況呢？成功了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定成功了吧？讓我見見他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.45,0:17:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快說 大夫 我爸的病房在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在二樓..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:38.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.42,0:17:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.54,0:17:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下午5點就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請探視人員盡早做好離院準備
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.34,0:17:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猛男同學 砂川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.08,0:17:57.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個 因為沒時間所以數量完全不夠..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.54,0:18:01.76,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.02,0:18:01.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有勞了 手術已經成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.17,0:18:05.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.42,0:18:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢 砂川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.66,0:18:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然去了天文館
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:15.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我還是太在意所以就過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.48,0:18:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和 今天很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.39,0:18:23.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看了這張寫計劃的紙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.94,0:18:25.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發現上面有好多擦掉重寫的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.73,0:18:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一想到猛男同學這麼用盡心思..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.77,0:18:35.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就好高興 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.89,0:18:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 今天我過了最棒的生日哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.84,0:18:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和 我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我全心全意喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 猛男同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.67,0:18:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這是喜極而泣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.67,0:19:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.98,0:19:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.71,0:19:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要女朋友嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.53,0:19:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.15,0:19:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砂川同學 我可以介紹你我學校的同學哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 拜託你什麼都別做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽我說 一直關係融洽的人就是最合得來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.65,0:19:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.66,0:19:19.25,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為像猛男同學那樣的女生很適合砂川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.79,0:19:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 像我一樣的女子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:27.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是怎樣的女子啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.90,0:19:31.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會找找看像猛男同學一樣的女生的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.86,0:19:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂是個好男人 所以對方一定也會喜歡上他的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.97,0:19:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來就能進行雙重約會了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 這主意真不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.00,0:19:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你們快停下..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充滿愛意的每一天很不錯哦 阿砂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.51,0:19:57.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.23,0:19:58.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屁股之松
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:07.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.82,0:20:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.38,0:20:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼不把大和同學一起帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.86,0:20:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 總有天想讓她也來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊 小時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.12,0:20:18.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在還沒搬來之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.83,0:20:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並不是很喜歡夕陽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.39,0:20:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺看著讓人很不安呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.55,0:20:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟那個點肚子正好也餓起來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.77,0:20:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂 阿砂 看天 看天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.20,0:20:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看著好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.43,0:20:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃不了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂 阿砂 你知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.31,0:20:47.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太陽下山後會變得很冷耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.32,0:20:54.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂 糟了 到晚上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:58.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小學規定要在4點回家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.79,0:21:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可回過神來已經太陽下山 變成晚上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.87,0:21:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿砂 糟了 糟了 阿砂..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直沒發現嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.84,0:21:08.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過啊 來這裡之後就再沒有不安過了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太陽下山後果然很冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.72,0:21:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.98,0:21:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:20.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
